<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contact</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@5.15.4/css/fontawesome.min.css"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/2.4.1/semantic.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-8bHTC73gkZ7rZ7vpqUQThUDhqcNFyYi2xgDgPDHc+GXVGHXq+xPjynxIopALmOPqzo9JZj0k6OqqewdGO3EsrQ=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    
    <!-- bootstrap esential -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles-homepage.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/contact.css" />

    <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/894924603a.js"></script>
    <%- include('partials/favicon'); %> <%-
    include('partials/scriptbootstrap');%>

    <!-- chestii pt multiselect dropdown -->

    <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <%- include('partials/dropdown'); %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <section class="contact-header">
      <nav>
        <a href="/"> <%- include("partials/logo") %> </a>
        <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
          <i class="fa fa-times" onclick="hideMenu()"></i>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/">ACASA</a></li>
            <li>
              <a href="/universitati">UNIVERSITATI</a>
            </li>
            <li><a href="/despre">DESPRE NOI</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <i class="fa fa-bars" onclick="showMenu()"></i>
      </nav>

      <h1>Contacteaza-ne</h1>
    </section>

    <div class="desc container">
      <h3>
        Lasati-ne un mesaj cu sugestii si pareri cu privire la platforma UniRo.
      </h3>
      <h5>
        Mesajele de la dumneavoastra ne sunt de ajutor in dezvoltarea platformei
        pe viitor, precum si cu introducerea de universitati noi.
      </h5>
    </div>

    <section>
      <div class="contact-form container">
        <div class="forms">
          <ul class="nav nav-tabs select" id="myTab" role="tablist">
            <li class="nav-item buton-select" role="presentation">
              <button
                class="nav-link active"
                id="home-tab"
                data-bs-toggle="tab"
                data-bs-target="#home"
                type="button"
                role="tab"
                aria-controls="home"
                aria-selected="true"
              >
                Utilizator platforma
              </button>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item buton-select" role="presentation">
              <button
                class="nav-link"
                id="contact-tab"
                data-bs-toggle="tab"
                data-bs-target="#contact"
                type="button"
                role="tab"
                aria-controls="contact"
                aria-selected="false"
              >
                Reprezentant universitate
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
            <div
              class="tab-pane fade show active"
              id="home"
              role="tabpanel"
              aria-labelledby="home-tab"
            >
              <%- include('partials/userForm.ejs')%>
            </div>

            <div
              class="tab-pane fade"
              id="contact"
              role="tabpanel"
              aria-labelledby="contact-tab"
            >
              <%- include('partials/uniForm.ejs')%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://smtpjs.com/v3/smtp.js"></script>
    <script src="scripts/email.js"></script>
    <script src="scripts/menu.js"></script>
    <script>
      $("#materiiSelect").dropdown();
      $("#specializariSelect").dropdown();
      $("#oras").dropdown();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
